%hive

select age, gender_cd, category from webloganalytics where age is not NULL LIMIT 1000

%md

Interesting. It looks like the majority of our users come into the range of 20-30 years old. We also seems to have somewhat even split between men and women in that range. However as we go furthur down the specctrum the data seems kewed and not as normal. Females tend to dominate the older ages, except for at the age of 50. Interesting!

------

Finally, we'll take a look at the interest categories of our users and how those are distributed.
